cu.explanation_en: Setting SCTP instreams to 0 is out of range for valid values and will cause SCTP association failure, preventing F1 interface communication.

du.explanation_en: Setting SCTP instreams to 0 is out of range for valid values and will cause SCTP association failure, preventing F1 interface communication.
du.explanation_zh: 將 SCTP 輸入流設定為 0 超出有效值範圍，會導致 SCTP 關聯失敗，阻止 F1 介面通訊。
